{
  "stem": "27770.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because I was in this barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, between all the people who arrived to Auschwitz, as they say, from 22 nations people arrived, only the Jew was selected.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Any other person who died, died a natural death.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you died from a sickness, if you died from weakness, if you died from a cold, if you had to come to the hospital, he arrived to a hospital.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You had to give them help in a hospital, whatever they had there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But selected were only the Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Later, by the end, was the Gypsies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So as we are here today, in America, and all over the world, we Jews, we should know one thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If you are a Zionist, if you have feeling to Israel or not, you should know one thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Only two people were destroyed in life in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And those were the Jews and the Gypsies, because they didn't have a country.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So when we think about Israel, and we think to give something back for the Arabs or take all these lies from Arafat, and he only wants the south part or the east part from Jerusalem, this is all lies.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He wants to take over Israel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "All the Arabs, they want to take over Israel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because, if you would come an Indian, right now, who was born and his great-great-father was born in America, and who come to Washington, we say, now, we want to have the east part of Washington should be our capital.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What would say our government?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Get the hell out of here, right?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Would you talk about it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Would you discuss it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Americans are only 500 years in this country since Columbus.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why don't they give them a part from Washington for a capital town?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because it's nonsense.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
